        {
            "title": "亞洲股市因伊朗局勢緊張而下滑;日經指數與韓國綜合指數自高位回落",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BRszR18v9Fmhfmzao.B1Hw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB380HB_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲股市下跌,在波動交易中逆轉早盤漲勢,儘管科技股財報強勁,但持續的美伊緊張局勢令投資者保持謹慎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">區域市場開盤走高,追隨華爾街隔夜漲勢,標普500指數和納斯達克指數在總統唐納德·川普延長與伊朗的停火協議後收於歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,在霍爾木茲海峽最近發生事件後,全球石油供應面臨風險,樂觀情緒消退。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股指期貨在亞洲交易時段下滑。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>日經指數突破60,000點;韓國綜合指數創新高</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本日經225指數下跌1.1%,報58,952.1點,此前盤中觸及60,198.0點的歷史新高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-33720ba8-6d90-3590-ad91-3034732d84b1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國綜合指數下跌0.5%,報6,384.29點,此前觸及6,557.76點的高峰,受科技股強勢支撐。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在SK海力士(KS:000660)公布亮眼財報後,晶片製造商支撐了市場走勢。這家英偉達(NASDAQ:NVDA)供應商公布第一季營業利潤增長超過五倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一業績受到高頻寬記憶體和其他用於人工智慧應用晶片的強勁需求推動,全球科技公司正在加大數據中心投資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SK海力士(KS:000660)股價在早盤觸及歷史新高後小幅下跌。三星電子(KS:005930)股價上漲2.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國經濟數據也提振了市場情緒。亞洲第四大經濟體第一季增長快於預期,國內生產總值季度環比增長1.7%,超過約0.9%的預測,而年度增長加速至約3.6%,遠高於預期。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>儘管停火延長,美伊緊張局勢仍持續</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於霍爾木茲海峽的供應仍然中斷,油價維持在每桶100美元上方,接近近期高點,市場情緒依然脆弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗週三在川普宣布停火協議後數小時內在霍爾木茲海峽扣押了兩艘商船,凸顯停火協議的脆弱性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國上證綜合指數和藍籌股滬深300指數均下跌0.5%,香港恆生指數下跌1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外,澳洲標普/澳交所200指數和新加坡海峽時報指數均下跌1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與印度Nifty 50指數掛鉤的期貨下跌0.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%9B%A0%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E7%B7%8A%E5%BC%B5%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%93%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%88%87%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%9C%E5%90%88%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%87%AA%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-041753051.html",
